Yeah, I understand,
but this is

362
00:20:50,223 --> 00:20:52,073
something I need.

363
00:20:56,529 --> 00:20:57,913
So...

364
00:20:59,749 --> 00:21:01,416
What do I call you?

365
00:21:03,419 --> 00:21:05,704
Diggle's good.

366
00:21:05,706 --> 00:21:07,122
Dig if you want.

367
00:21:07,124 --> 00:21:08,456
You're ex-military?

368
00:21:08,458 --> 00:21:09,741
Yes, sir.
105th airborne

369
