00:25:47,271 --> 00:25:51,273
That maniac put two
of my men in the hospital.

418
00:25:51,275 --> 00:25:52,608
Well, thanks
for your statement.

419
00:25:52,610 --> 00:25:57,329
We'll put out an APB
