527
00:32:05,682 --> 00:32:09,401
but this time,
it will be worse.

528
00:32:09,403 --> 00:32:11,403
Got to roll.

529
00:32:11,405 --> 00:32:16,241
I got 5 years of
debauchery to catch up on

530
