00:37:16,106 --> 00:37:17,856
and Hunt getting robbed
right next door

591
00:37:17,858 --> 00:37:21,493
and by the same guy who
rescued us at the warehouse.

592
00:37:21,495 --> 00:37:23,162
If I were you,
Tommy,

593
00:37:23,164 --> 00:37:25,581
I'd just be glad
you're alive.

594
00:37:25,583 --> 00:37:28,700
